Colleen Shannon (born April 14, 1978) is known as Playboy magazine's Playmate of the Month for January 2004 and the magazine's 50th anniversary Playmate.
Shannon was Playboy's 50th Anniversary Playmate in 2004.
She has DJ'd at Harrah's Atlantic City, the Seminole Hard Rock Hotel and Casino Tampa, and LG Fashion Week.
Shannon was arrested in August 2012 for smuggling her Canadian boyfriend, Robert Skojo, into the United States.
She pleaded guilty in June 2013 of illegally "transporting an alien".
In October 2013, she was sentenced to four months in United States Federal Prison and to pay a $5,000 fine.
